Description.BulletDescription:

AMD Ryzen 7 5800H processor: The AMD Ryzen 7 5800H is a processor for big (gaming) laptops based on the Cezanne generation. The R7 5800H integrates all eight cores based on the Zen 3 microarchitecture. They are clocked at 2.8 (guaranteed base clock) to 4.4 GHz (Turbo) and support SMT / Hyperthreading (16 threads). The chip is manufactured in the modern 7 nm process at TSMC. Compared to the 5800H (up to 54 W), the 5800HS is configured to a TDP of 35W.

Bundle with wireless mouse: Bundled with a wireless mouse that offers smooth and precise navigation.
